node.text: … It took a lot for me to do this. 💯 I’m not proud of a lot of decisions I’ve made in the past but I’m ready to let the truth off my chest and move forward happily with my Wife after I feel Like God has touched me and made me a better Man. DROPPING TODAY ON YOUTUBE CARMEN AND COREY CHANNEL 6PM Central time stay tuned…..
